44918","@type":"sc:Dataset","name":"IMDb Top Movies 1980-2026","url":"https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/elvisbui/imdb-top-movies-1980-2026/versions/1","description":"Every feature movie on IMDb released from 1980 onward with at least 5,000 user votes. Sourced from IMDb\u0027s official non-commercial datasets (\u0060title.basics\u0060 and \u0060title.ratings\u0060) on April 28, 2026.\n\nOne row per movie. Includes title, original title, year, runtime, comma-separated genres, IMDb average rating, vote count, and the canonical IMDb URL. Sorted by vote count descending, so the most-watched and most-discussed movies are at the top.\n\nFiltered to non-adult feature films only \u2014 TV series, shorts, and X-rated content excluded.\n\n## Columns\n\n| Column | Description |\n|---|---|\n| imdb_id | IMDb tconst identifier (e.g. tt0111161 for The Shawshank Redemption) |\n| title | Primary title (English where applicable) |\n| original_title | Original-language title |\n| year | Release year |\n| runtime_minutes | Runtime in minutes |\n| genres | Comma-separated IMDb genre tags |\n| average_rating | IMDb weighted average rating (0-10) |\n| num_votes | Total user votes counted in the rating |\n| imdb_url | https://www.imdb.com/title/"}